title: Milo Yiannopoulos Resigns From Breitbart News!
text:
It seemed like it was only a matter of time.
After his most recent controversy which involved basically endorsing pedophilia, Milo Yiannopoulos is officially done at Breitbart News .
We'd heard the self-promoting provocateur was on his way out of the company, but now it's official.
